WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.110
Praise the Lord. Let's start.

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:04.710
We waited for a little

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:06.550
bit for you all to come on before I start

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:09.270
talking, but thank you for joining us.

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:12.150
Good morning, family. Good evening,

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:14.789
wherever you are all around the world.

00:00:14.799 --> 00:00:17.189
Thank you for joining us again today; we

00:00:17.199 --> 00:00:18.870
really appreciate it. We're going to

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.710
pray, and we'll just go tubing tonight

00:00:20.720 --> 00:00:22.470
and talk about some of the things

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:25.349
that we're seeing in the news.

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:27.109
I'll go over some of the things the Lord

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:29.589
said to me today

00:00:29.599 --> 00:00:34.630
when I was driving around.

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:37.750
He

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:40.709
talked to me about William Seymour

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:43.590
and the box that

00:00:43.600 --> 00:00:45.990
he used to place on his head before

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.190
every single meeting. He would sit

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.910
in the corner of the room with the

00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:55.270
box on his head for sometimes up

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:58.389
to an hour, sometimes less, depending on

00:00:58.399 --> 00:01:01.830
how long the Lord told him to do it.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:03.110
The Lord said to me,

00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:07.429
'Brandon, my people must find their box.

00:01:07.439 --> 00:01:10.630
You must find your

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:10.640
box.'What

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:12.789
is your box?

00:01:12.799 --> 00:01:13.910
That's what he started talking to me

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:16.390
about.

00:01:16.400 --> 00:01:17.910
I said, 'Well, what do you

00:01:17.910 --> 00:01:17.920
mean?'He

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:20.390
said, 'I will not share my

00:01:20.400 --> 00:01:22.710
glory with anybody for what's about to

00:01:22.720 --> 00:01:25.350
take place in this last outpouring.

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:28.550
I will not share my glory with

00:01:28.550 --> 00:01:28.560
anybody.'William

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:31.830
Seymour, before the

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:33.510
service would start and the glory would

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:36.710
start, would find that

00:01:36.720 --> 00:01:40.149
place of death to himself:

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:41.749
humility,

00:01:41.749 --> 00:01:41.759
humbling

00:01:41.759 --> 00:01:43.510
yourself underneath the mighty

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:45.429
hand of the Lord.

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:47.429
So he started talking to me about

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:50.069
putting the box on. He said,

00:01:50.069 --> 00:01:50.079
'Brandon,

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:51.510
I'm not going to tell you what the box

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:54.389
is for you; you'll have to figure it out

00:01:54.399 --> 00:01:56.230
yourself.'But

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:58.870
a box is not just lip service,

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:01.670
telling people that it is

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:05.350
not you concerning the glory; it's a

00:02:05.360 --> 00:02:07.670
heart thing.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.550
He said, 'I'm looking at the

00:02:10.550 --> 00:02:10.560
heart—not

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:11.910
just what

00:02:11.920 --> 00:02:13.830
words say.'There are so many preachers,

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:15.110
he said, who get on the stage and

00:02:15.120 --> 00:02:17.270
say, 'We give you all the glory,

00:02:17.270 --> 00:02:17.280
we

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.030
give you all the honor, and

00:02:19.030 --> 00:02:19.040
we

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:21.030
give you all the praise,'but their

00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:24.550
heart is all about themselves

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:26.470
and they don't have the box on their

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:28.470
head.

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:30.710
He said, 'The bigger the box, the more

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:33.589
freedom I will give you.

00:02:33.599 --> 00:02:36.790
The larger the box,

00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:36.800
it's

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:38.390
like being in a

00:02:38.400 --> 00:02:40.470
refrigerator box.

00:02:40.480 --> 00:02:42.150
You have a lot more room to move around

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:44.229
in there; there's a lot more space to do

00:02:44.239 --> 00:02:47.670
things. But the smaller the box,

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:51.509
the less the trust, as you

00:02:51.509 --> 00:02:51.519
must always

00:02:51.519 --> 00:02:54.550
deflect to give

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:56.630
him the glory for what's about to take

00:02:59.599 --> 00:03:02.309
place.'He

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:07.990
talked to me about Sister Kuhlman, Kathryn

00:03:07.990 --> 00:03:08.000
Kuhlman, and

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:10.229
how she would

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:11.830
always give him the glory, but it was

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:13.910
always from the heart. The moment

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:16.550
people started to

00:03:16.560 --> 00:03:19.270
try to uplift her or tell her how great

00:03:19.280 --> 00:03:22.790
she was, she would recluse

00:03:22.800 --> 00:03:25.350
because she realized the source of the

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:29.670
power and the source of the glory was him.

00:03:29.680 --> 00:03:32.390
As long as

00:03:32.400 --> 00:03:34.149
the glory is

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:36.470
manifesting through you, you're a

00:03:36.480 --> 00:03:38.390
container, you're a vessel. He's moving

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:40.949
through you, but it's always to

00:03:40.959 --> 00:03:45.030
deflect to him.

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:47.350
The box represents

00:03:47.350 --> 00:03:47.360
dying

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:49.509
to self. The

00:03:49.519 --> 00:03:52.949
Apostle Paul said, 'I die

00:03:52.949 --> 00:03:52.959
daily.'The

00:03:52.959 --> 00:03:54.949
Lord started saying

00:03:54.949 --> 00:03:54.959
that

00:03:54.959 --> 00:03:58.229
to die daily is a

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:02.390
place of humility.

00:04:02.400 --> 00:04:04.070
It's not something that you have to

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:05.830
convince yourself of.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:08.149
No, you

00:04:08.149 --> 00:04:08.159
die

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:10.149
daily. The more I

00:04:10.159 --> 00:04:12.630
use you and the greater the glory

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:14.710
on your life, the more you have to find

00:04:14.720 --> 00:04:17.990
the box

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:20.629
to deflect.

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:22.469
The more you're accurate and the more

00:04:22.479 --> 00:04:24.950
things come to pass in the

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:29.510
days ahead, you're always to deflect.

00:04:29.520 --> 00:04:32.310
I always go back to

00:04:32.310 --> 00:04:32.320
it—and

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:34.230
I do it for myself

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.749
because it's really true—I'm

00:04:37.749 --> 00:04:37.759
just

00:04:37.759 --> 00:04:39.749
the janitor, which I was just a couple

00:04:39.749 --> 00:04:39.759
of

00:04:39.759 --> 00:04:41.749
years ago.

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:45.350
No matter if the president, a senator, or the head of whatever country is watching

00:04:52.639 --> 00:04:55.030
your channel and

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:58.150
they get their information and use

00:04:58.160 --> 00:05:00.150
it, it's not

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:02.603
mine; it's the Lord's.

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:06.070
The Lord was really

00:05:06.080 --> 00:05:09.029
telling me what's about to take place in

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:11.990
the days ahead with the church. He

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:13.270
said, 'You're about to see something

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:15.830
that you've never seen before,

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:19.430
and there's nothing to compare it to.

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:21.110
You're about to see something that

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:24.629
you've always longed for,

00:05:24.639 --> 00:05:26.870
what the elders always longed for, but

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:29.510
there's really nothing to compare it to.

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:32.629
For I'm going to do something unusual,

00:05:32.639 --> 00:05:36.230
son.

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:37.830
It will be something that we've never

00:05:37.840 --> 00:05:40.070
seen, and I'm not a cookie-cutter.'There

00:05:40.070 --> 00:05:40.080
are

00:05:40.080 --> 00:05:42.870
so many times we

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:44.550
come on here and take communion and

00:05:44.560 --> 00:05:47.430
have a pattern, and I tell you

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:48.790
things that the Lord is

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:51.270
showing us,

00:05:51.270 --> 00:05:51.280
but

00:05:51.280 --> 00:05:53.110
the Holy

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:54.629
Spirit

00:05:54.639 --> 00:05:57.590
has free

00:05:57.600 --> 00:06:01.189
reign to do whatever he wants to do.

00:06:01.199 --> 00:06:03.350
He used a word that

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:04.710
I didn't even know the

00:06:04.710 --> 00:06:04.720
meaning of.

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:06.950
What was the word?

00:06:06.960 --> 00:06:07.990
Status quo?

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:09.110
No, no,

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:11.990
no.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:15.430
Ask your mother.

00:06:15.440 --> 00:06:17.990
He used a word and said,

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:20.629
'Don't ever do this.'I said,

00:06:20.639 --> 00:06:22.230
'What does that even

00:06:22.230 --> 00:06:22.240
mean?'So

00:06:22.240 --> 00:06:25.270
Diana had to look it up. As

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:29.350
we were

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:31.110
being instructed by the Holy Spirit

00:06:31.120 --> 00:06:34.230
today, I thought, 'What's

00:06:34.240 --> 00:06:36.710
your

00:06:37.280 --> 00:06:38.150
box?'Anomaly.

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:45.510
Don't become an anomaly. There are so

00:06:45.520 --> 00:06:48.390
many people that have become an anomaly. I

00:06:48.390 --> 00:06:48.400
didn't

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.230
even know

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:53.110
what an anomaly was, but whenever he

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.110
uses big words like that,

00:06:55.120 --> 00:06:57.270
it goes with

00:06:57.280 --> 00:06:59.270
everything he's been saying. But I

00:06:59.280 --> 00:07:05.510
want you to know we must find the box.

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:08.070
The greater the glory and the greater the

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:08.080
platform,

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:10.469
the greater

00:07:10.479 --> 00:07:14.469
the death. He said that

00:07:14.469 --> 00:07:14.479
the light

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:17.990
afflictions

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:20.469
bring forth the greater glory.

00:07:20.469 --> 00:07:20.479
This

00:07:20.479 --> 00:07:23.909
refining—we

00:07:23.919 --> 00:07:25.589
have this treasure in

00:07:25.589 --> 00:07:25.599
earthen

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:27.189
vessels so that the excellency of the power is

00:07:27.199 --> 00:07:29.670
known of him and not of us.

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:31.830
It's more than you'll ever know—that to

00:07:31.840 --> 00:07:34.629
sustain what God has called us to do in

00:07:34.639 --> 00:07:37.510
these last days is to continually give

00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:41.110
him the glory for what he's doing.

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:43.990
Regardless,

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:46.150
because of insecurity and because

00:07:46.160 --> 00:07:50.390
people deal with

00:07:50.390 --> 00:07:50.400
flesh—our

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:54.070
flesh likes praise just like the devil; he

00:07:54.080 --> 00:07:56.150
wanted praise in heaven.

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:58.070
He said, 'I'll exalt myself

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:01.990
above the Lord,'and boy, did he

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.070
sure mess up.

00:08:04.080 --> 00:08:06.629
But our flesh always cries out for more

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:08.790
because maybe you were the kid the bully in the schoolyard

00:08:08.790 --> 00:08:08.800
was

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:10.550
always picking on or the

00:08:10.560 --> 00:08:14.790
last pick at sports.

00:08:17.199 --> 00:08:20.390
It's always nice

00:08:20.390 --> 00:08:20.400
for

00:08:20.400 --> 00:08:22.070
somebody to say, 'Well done, you

00:08:22.080 --> 00:08:24.469
did a good job.'But the

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:27.909
Lord was showing me that for what is coming, there

00:08:27.909 --> 00:08:27.919
are

00:08:27.919 --> 00:08:29.990
so many of you who watch this

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:32.230
channel

00:08:32.230 --> 00:08:32.240
and

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:34.469
are excited about this

00:08:34.469 --> 00:08:34.479
end-time

00:08:34.479 --> 00:08:36.949
outpouring. I have this revival

00:08:36.959 --> 00:08:39.589
behind me right now

00:08:39.599 --> 00:08:41.750
because one of the greatest moves of God

00:08:41.760 --> 00:08:44.149
this world has ever seen is about

00:08:44.159 --> 00:08:46.070
to hit from shore to shore, all around

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:48.550
this world.

00:08:48.560 --> 00:08:50.870
He'll choose individual

00:08:50.870 --> 00:08:50.880
people—the

00:08:50.880 --> 00:08:53.030
new Davids, the new Esthers,

00:08:53.030 --> 00:08:53.040
and the

00:08:53.040 --> 00:08:55.430
new leaders of this

00:08:55.430 --> 00:08:55.440
generation—to

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:57.750
take the baton and run and bring in

00:08:57.760 --> 00:09:00.230
the greatest harvest. But the Lord told

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.750
me, 'I want you to tell my

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:04.630
people: find your box like William

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:06.560
Seymour.'It

00:09:08.880 --> 00:09:11.590
doesn't have to be a physical box, but what's

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:14.630
your box?

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:18.470
William Seymour's was a

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:22.870
real box, and he

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:25.269
put that crate on his head.

00:09:25.279 --> 00:09:29.590
But he said, 'What's your

00:09:29.590 --> 00:09:29.600
box?'It's

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:31.829
the place of surrender, the

00:09:31.839 --> 00:09:34.550
place of death, the place to humble

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:36.310
yourself underneath the mighty hand of

00:09:36.320 --> 00:09:38.550
the Lord. We have the treasure in

00:09:38.550 --> 00:09:38.560
earthen

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:40.790
vessels

00:09:40.790 --> 00:09:40.800
so

00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.389
that the excellency of the power will be

00:09:42.399 --> 00:09:45.110
known of him.

00:09:45.120 --> 00:09:47.269
He will not share his glory with any of

00:09:47.279 --> 00:09:49.430
us.

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:53.590
Regardless of how amazing things

00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:53.600
are

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:56.230
with the words

00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:57.910
and things that happen in the days

00:09:57.920 --> 00:10:00.790
ahead, I always want you to know that

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:04.310
Brandon

00:10:04.310 --> 00:10:04.320
Biggs

00:10:04.320 --> 00:10:06.150
is just a servant of the Most High God,

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:10.550
just like you are.

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:12.310
It's so important

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:17.750
that you stay the janitor in your eyes.

00:10:17.760 --> 00:10:21.110
Don't lose sight of yourself.

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:23.910
The Lord always says to stay grounded.

00:10:23.920 --> 00:10:26.870
Keep your feet on the ground.

00:10:26.880 --> 00:10:28.710
Remember,

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:31.509
even today, put your feet on the ground.

00:10:31.519 --> 00:10:33.670
I was driving and I said, 'What does

00:10:33.680 --> 00:10:36.310
that

00:10:36.310 --> 00:10:36.320
mean?'Ground

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:38.710
yourself.

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:45.030
Look inside. Go deep within.

00:10:45.040 --> 00:10:46.710
This is nothing compared to what I want

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:49.750
to do in the days ahead with you.

00:10:49.760 --> 00:10:51.350
This is nothing compared to what I want

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:53.269
to do with me and each one of

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:55.110
these individuals that are here praying with

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:59.829
you.

00:10:59.839 --> 00:11:01.590
There are so many souls that are about

00:11:01.600 --> 00:11:04.230
to come into the kingdom of God, and

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:06.069
there's so much arrogance and so much

00:11:06.079 --> 00:11:09.110
pride behind the pulpits.

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:10.470
The Lord said, 'Brandon, I'm going to

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:13.190
humble the church. There's

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:14.630
going to be a cleansing. There's going

00:11:14.640 --> 00:11:17.269
to be a 1 Corinthians 5:5 moment. You're going

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:19.990
to see these things in the days

00:11:19.990 --> 00:11:20.000
ahead.'And

00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:22.310
the young Davids,

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:24.790
the new voices that I have for this hour

00:11:24.800 --> 00:11:26.949
will rise up and they will take the

00:11:26.959 --> 00:11:29.509
baton from the elders.

00:11:29.519 --> 00:11:31.190
There'll be new Esthers. There'll be these

00:11:31.200 --> 00:11:32.949
new voices that seemingly

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:35.590
came out of nowhere. He said, 'I will

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:38.470
use them greatly in the days

00:11:38.470 --> 00:11:38.480
ahead.'But

00:11:38.480 --> 00:11:40.069
you've not even entered into the second

00:11:40.079 --> 00:11:41.750
phase of what I've called you to do yet.

00:11:44.160 --> 00:11:45.990
Signs and wonders will follow them that

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:48.470
believe.

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.230
He said, 'I don't want you to do

00:11:50.240 --> 00:11:54.310
videos so much until I tell you to. I

00:11:54.320 --> 00:11:56.150
want you to be more strategic in the way

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:58.870
you do things in prayer.

00:11:58.880 --> 00:12:00.949
Do it this way and do it

00:12:00.949 --> 00:12:00.959
exactly.'He's

00:12:00.959 --> 00:12:02.310
given me great

00:12:02.320 --> 00:12:04.470
instruction for us to pray together and

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:06.870
how we are supposed to function as an

00:12:06.880 --> 00:12:10.310
army. As we flow in the army, as we

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:12.069
flow with the anointing of the Holy

00:12:12.079 --> 00:12:14.949
Ghost, we will have great results.

00:12:14.959 --> 00:12:17.190
With great power comes great

00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:19.190
responsibility.

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:25.350
They stole that from the Lord, I

00:12:25.360 --> 00:12:28.629
guarantee you.

00:12:28.639 --> 00:12:31.190
I always want

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:32.870
to tell you all this because it's very

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:36.069
important that

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:40.790
you understand he is a good

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:43.110
God and he loves you, but he'll not share

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:45.269
his glory with anybody. Many

00:12:45.279 --> 00:12:47.990
of you have major calls

00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:49.910
on your life,

00:12:49.920 --> 00:12:53.110
and

00:12:53.120 --> 00:12:54.550
it's so interesting because so

00:12:54.560 --> 00:12:57.030
many of you email saying, 'I had this

00:12:57.030 --> 00:12:57.040
vision'or

00:12:57.040 --> 00:12:59.430
'I had this

00:12:59.430 --> 00:12:59.440
dream.'You

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:01.990
have so much

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.750
potential, but you're not

00:13:03.760 --> 00:13:07.030
dead to yourself.

00:13:07.040 --> 00:13:09.110
There's so much ego and so much stuff

00:13:09.120 --> 00:13:14.069
going on. I said, 'Find the

00:13:14.069 --> 00:13:14.079
janitor.'No

00:13:14.079 --> 00:13:15.990
matter how much you feel that you

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:18.230
should have a platform or wonder

00:13:18.230 --> 00:13:18.240
why

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:21.350
God is not using you yet, find

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:24.550
the place of death.

00:13:24.560 --> 00:13:28.150
Find the janitor. You

00:13:28.150 --> 00:13:28.160
might say,

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:30.150
'I'm a cleaner now, I do this and

00:13:30.150 --> 00:13:30.160
that,'but

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:31.750
the Lord said,

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:35.509
'Find the janitor

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:39.110
and die there

00:13:39.120 --> 00:13:43.190
to

00:13:43.190 --> 00:13:43.200
yourself.'I

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:44.790
don't know how else to describe that

00:13:44.800 --> 00:13:46.710
to you; you have to figure it out

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:49.884
yourself. The more you squirm,

00:13:49.894 --> 00:13:51.030
it's like someone

00:13:51.030 --> 00:13:51.040
who

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:53.509
lays a sacrifice on the altar

00:13:55.839 --> 00:13:58.389
to the Father. My life is for

00:13:58.399 --> 00:14:00.550
His. You're up there and

00:14:01.839 --> 00:14:03.430
He's looking to see if you're

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:05.750
dead. You say, 'I'm dead,'but

00:14:05.750 --> 00:14:05.760
the Lord

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.670
looks and

00:14:07.670 --> 00:14:07.680
says,

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:09.030
'No, you're not dead yet.'You

00:14:09.030 --> 00:14:09.040
keep saying,

00:14:09.040 --> 00:14:11.030
'I'm

00:14:11.040 --> 00:14:12.550
dead,'but

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:14.150
you're

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:15.509
just looking around like a

00:14:15.509 --> 00:14:15.519
kid

00:14:15.519 --> 00:14:17.590
playing.

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:20.310
When you're truly dead, you'll know it.

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:21.910
There's no pretending.

00:14:21.920 --> 00:14:23.829
Dead

00:14:23.829 --> 00:14:23.839
is

00:14:23.839 --> 00:14:27.219
dead, and the flesh starts to stink.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:31.750
You'll know it.

00:14:43.600 --> 00:14:47.189
It's a place of surrender.

00:14:47.199 --> 00:14:49.430
It's a place of saying, 'Father, I'm not going

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:51.189
to complain about what you have for me

00:14:51.199 --> 00:14:53.350
anymore, no matter if this whole thing

00:14:53.360 --> 00:14:56.150
goes away tomorrow.'Between all the

00:14:56.160 --> 00:14:58.069
invitations I get to

00:14:58.079 --> 00:15:01.430
preach from all around the globe—some in Australia

00:15:01.430 --> 00:15:01.440
and South America—the Australian

00:15:01.440 --> 00:15:04.230
one

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:11.590
was

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:13.509
tempting because it

00:15:13.509 --> 00:15:13.519
would

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:15.670
be fun to go way down under

00:15:15.680 --> 00:15:17.910
and see what's down there.

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:20.389
But I won't do it until the

00:15:20.399 --> 00:15:23.269
Lord says. It's interesting

00:15:23.279 --> 00:15:26.389
because I

00:15:26.399 --> 00:15:28.550
told Diana that the more everything

00:15:28.560 --> 00:15:30.629
takes place, the

00:15:30.639 --> 00:15:34.150
more I just want to be reclusive.

00:15:43.839 --> 00:15:46.230
Change happens so quickly for all of us.

00:15:46.240 --> 00:15:48.230
The Lord

00:15:48.240 --> 00:15:50.150
will

00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:53.110
put his finger on you, and the moment he

00:15:53.120 --> 00:15:55.110
does, he says, 'Brandon, I don't

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:57.030
want anyone to get the glory for what

00:15:57.040 --> 00:15:59.269
I'm about to do in your life. There's no

00:15:59.279 --> 00:16:01.590
platform that will ever be given to you.

00:16:01.600 --> 00:16:04.550
It'll all be by my hand. The money

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:07.509
I bless you with, the notoriety,

00:16:07.519 --> 00:16:10.069
everything

00:16:10.079 --> 00:16:13.670
will come from me.

00:16:13.680 --> 00:16:17.110
Just bring in my

00:16:17.110 --> 00:16:17.120
harvest.'All

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:20.310
that to say this:

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:22.629
Braden has some of these clips

00:16:22.639 --> 00:16:24.069
and he'll show you this, and we'll

00:16:24.079 --> 00:16:25.829
go right into tubing. That's really

00:16:25.839 --> 00:16:27.269
what He's been talking to me about the

00:16:27.279 --> 00:16:29.509
last couple of days. He gave me

00:16:29.509 --> 00:16:29.519
a

00:16:29.519 --> 00:16:33.030
scripture.

00:16:33.040 --> 00:16:35.670
I was watching Sister Kuhlman

00:16:35.670 --> 00:16:35.680
and

00:16:35.680 --> 00:16:39.189
she said her

00:16:39.199 --> 00:16:42.069
main thing with the

00:16:42.079 --> 00:16:50.790
Lord

00:16:50.800 --> 00:16:55.189
is Psalm 17:8:

00:16:55.199 --> 00:16:58.389
'Keep me as the apple of thy eye. Hide me

00:16:58.399 --> 00:17:02.069
under the shadow of thy

00:17:02.069 --> 00:17:02.079
wings.'Her

00:17:02.079 --> 00:17:05.510
description of that in

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:07.429
this sermon—and we can put the

00:17:07.439 --> 00:17:10.150
link below—is

00:17:10.150 --> 00:17:10.160
amazing.

00:17:10.160 --> 00:17:11.829
Braden,

00:17:11.839 --> 00:17:13.990
I'll send this to you so

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:15.829
you can show them this sermon. I would

00:17:15.839 --> 00:17:17.750
encourage everybody to listen to

00:17:17.750 --> 00:17:17.760
it.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:22.230
This guy has a YouTube

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:23.829
channel

00:17:23.829 --> 00:17:23.839
with

00:17:23.839 --> 00:17:27.029
3,000 subscribers.

00:17:27.039 --> 00:17:29.750
Diana found

00:17:29.750 --> 00:17:29.760
it.

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:33.190
Someone

00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:37.990
left him an attic full of Mrs.

00:17:37.990 --> 00:17:38.000
Kuhlman's

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:43.270
tapes, reel-to-reels,

00:17:43.270 --> 00:17:43.280
and

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:47.190
old stuff that has never been

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:52.310
public. There

00:17:52.310 --> 00:17:52.320
are

00:17:52.320 --> 00:17:55.190
recordings of someone

00:17:55.190 --> 00:17:55.200
in the audience

00:17:55.200 --> 00:18:00.549
in Ohio

00:18:02.320 --> 00:18:05.110
recording her.

00:18:05.120 --> 00:18:08.150
He's bringing

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:10.390
forth all

00:18:10.390 --> 00:18:10.400
this

00:18:10.400 --> 00:18:13.270
lost material, and these archives

00:18:13.280 --> 00:18:15.750
are

00:18:15.750 --> 00:18:15.760
life-changing.

00:18:15.760 --> 00:18:18.710
He

00:18:18.720 --> 00:18:21.510
has hundreds

00:18:21.520 --> 00:18:24.630
of boxes from a fan

00:18:24.630 --> 00:18:24.640
of Kathryn Kuhlman

00:18:24.640 --> 00:18:26.310
who just

00:18:26.320 --> 00:18:28.390
stored it in the attic.

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:30.789
Diana

00:18:30.799 --> 00:18:32.630
and

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:35.669
I

00:18:35.679 --> 00:18:37.750
feel like we're at a

00:18:37.760 --> 00:18:40.310
buffet. I'm going to

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.510
give this to you.

00:18:45.919 --> 00:18:47.510
I don't even think he

00:18:47.520 --> 00:18:49.590
knows who I am, but I watch his channel.

00:18:49.600 --> 00:18:51.110
It's not about him; it's

00:18:51.120 --> 00:18:53.430
about Katherine.

00:18:53.440 --> 00:18:56.630
I'll give you one sermon

00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:59.510
that is amazing;

00:18:59.520 --> 00:19:02.549
the scripture is 'The secret

00:19:02.559 --> 00:19:06.870
to success is loving

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:12.950
Him.'This

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:19.190
is how I keep myself full.

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:21.909
I'm a scavenger; I pick the bone

00:19:21.919 --> 00:19:24.390
until there's nothing

00:19:24.390 --> 00:19:24.400
left.

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:26.390
I told Diana we do

00:19:26.390 --> 00:19:26.400
this

00:19:26.400 --> 00:19:28.310
every year.

00:19:31.760 --> 00:19:33.110
Do you have that for them?

00:19:36.799 --> 00:19:39.029
Can you put it on

00:19:39.039 --> 00:19:40.549
there so they can see it?

00:19:44.320 --> 00:19:46.070
I

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:47.909
want them to grasp it

00:19:47.919 --> 00:19:50.390
because

00:19:50.400 --> 00:19:52.710
this will change your life if

00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:54.549
you listen.

00:19:57.919 --> 00:19:59.190
People

00:19:59.190 --> 00:19:59.200
ask

00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:01.110
me about these books;

00:20:01.120 --> 00:20:03.350
there

00:20:03.350 --> 00:20:03.360
it

00:20:03.360 --> 00:20:04.870
is:

00:20:04.870 --> 00:20:04.880
Oral

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:08.870
Roberts, 1972.

00:20:08.880 --> 00:20:11.190
Isn't that awesome?

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:13.430
Kenneth Hagin books. Things that will

00:20:13.440 --> 00:20:15.990
change your life.

00:20:16.000 --> 00:20:18.470
I don't know what his channel's

00:20:18.480 --> 00:20:21.830
name is. Kathryn

00:20:21.830 --> 00:20:21.840
Kuhlman

00:20:21.840 --> 00:20:25.750
Radio,

00:20:25.760 --> 00:20:27.990
no AI, because there's so many people

00:20:28.000 --> 00:20:31.029
trying to make fake AI sermons. And

00:20:31.039 --> 00:20:33.510
this is all her original archives of

00:20:33.520 --> 00:20:35.590
stuff that this guy stored up, so it

00:20:35.600 --> 00:20:38.710
will bless you. It's trying to help. If

00:20:38.720 --> 00:20:39.909
you want to listen to it, fine; if you

00:20:39.919 --> 00:20:42.870
don't, fine. But there you go.

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.789
When Diana found this, I went,

00:20:44.799 --> 00:20:47.669
"Oh my goodness, this blessed me

00:20:47.679 --> 00:20:51.669
so."I'll

00:20:51.679 --> 00:20:53.430
play a second of it so they

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:54.310
can hear it.

00:20:54.320 --> 00:20:55.830
I'll be right back.

00:20:56.720 --> 00:21:00.549
I dare say that practically every

00:21:03.039 --> 00:21:05.750
young person who is graduating

00:21:05.750 --> 00:21:05.760
today—every

00:21:05.760 --> 00:21:07.190
one of you young people who are

00:21:07.200 --> 00:21:10.470
wearing a cap and a gown—has come from a

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:13.350
Christian home.

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:14.950
If you've not come from a Christian

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:17.990
home, you've had the finest Christian

00:21:18.000 --> 00:21:21.029
training here at Oral Roberts

00:21:21.039 --> 00:21:22.710
University.

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:26.070
You know doctrine, you know your Bible.

00:21:26.080 --> 00:21:28.390
And for me to stand up here and preach a

00:21:28.400 --> 00:21:32.630
message, for me to give you doctrine,

00:21:32.640 --> 00:21:35.190
would be so foolish,

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:37.909
for nothing that I could say to you

00:21:37.919 --> 00:21:40.390
would be something you have not already

00:21:40.400 --> 00:21:46.149
heard and known.

00:21:46.159 --> 00:21:49.029
I just want to take the lid off of my

00:21:49.039 --> 00:21:50.789
heart

00:21:50.799 --> 00:21:56.390
for a few minutes.

00:21:56.400 --> 00:22:00.630
Two weeks ago,

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:02.870
I was in a music hall in Kansas City,

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:04.630
Missouri,

00:22:04.640 --> 00:22:08.390
and I got up early one morning

00:22:08.400 --> 00:22:12.789
and I drove 60 miles out of Kansas City

00:22:12.799 --> 00:22:15.909
to Concordia, Missouri, where

00:22:15.919 --> 00:22:21.830
I was born.

00:22:21.840 --> 00:22:28.390
And I did something:

00:22:28.400 --> 00:22:30.870
I went back to that little Methodist

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:35.270
church, and I was so shocked that it got

00:22:35.280 --> 00:22:40.710
so small in such a short time.

00:22:40.720 --> 00:22:44.710
When I was young, it looked so big.

00:22:44.720 --> 00:22:47.029
When I went back

00:22:47.039 --> 00:22:49.909
two weeks ago,

00:22:49.919 --> 00:22:53.990
the same pews were there.

00:22:54.000 --> 00:22:56.310
They were just as shiny as the Sunday

00:22:56.320 --> 00:22:59.430
morning when I was 14 years of age

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:01.190
and received that wonderful spiritual

00:23:01.200 --> 00:23:04.710
experience of being born again.

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:07.909
Walking into the vestibule,

00:23:07.919 --> 00:23:11.990
the rope was still there. A little tiny

00:23:12.000 --> 00:23:14.710
Methodist church, not seating any more

00:23:14.720 --> 00:23:17.750
than a hundred people—you could maybe

00:23:17.760 --> 00:23:23.270
squeeze 125 people in the church.

00:23:23.280 --> 00:23:26.470
Walking into that little vestibule,

00:23:26.480 --> 00:23:28.950
there was the rope

00:23:28.960 --> 00:23:32.789
that always rang the bell

00:23:32.799 --> 00:23:37.426
when somebody died in Concordia.

00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:41.590
If it was a young person, they tolled it

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:43.750
once.

00:23:43.760 --> 00:23:47.669
When it was

00:23:47.679 --> 00:23:49.669
a middle-aged person, they would toll

00:23:49.679 --> 00:23:53.270
the bell twice. If

00:23:53.270 --> 00:23:53.280
it

00:23:53.280 --> 00:23:55.270
was an elderly person, they would toll

00:23:55.280 --> 00:23:59.029
it three times. And then everybody ran

00:23:59.039 --> 00:24:01.029
to the telephone and asked the one

00:24:01.039 --> 00:24:06.230
telephone operator who died.

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:09.909
And the bell was still there

00:24:09.919 --> 00:24:13.830
and the rope was still there

00:24:13.840 --> 00:24:18.630
that had tolled for so many people.

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:21.830
And I walked in

00:24:21.840 --> 00:24:25.190
and I sat

00:24:25.200 --> 00:24:29.830
in the corner of the same pew,

00:24:29.840 --> 00:24:33.110
the third row from the front. I sat in

00:24:33.120 --> 00:24:38.230
that same corner of that pew that I sat

00:24:38.240 --> 00:24:40.870
that Sunday morning

00:24:40.870 --> 00:24:40.880
when

00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:46.149
I was only 14 years of age.

00:24:46.159 --> 00:24:49.269
It was the very first time that I had

00:24:49.279 --> 00:24:50.630
ever felt the power of the Holy Spirit.

00:24:50.640 --> 00:24:51.830
And I didn't recognize the power of the

00:24:51.840 --> 00:24:53.750
Holy Spirit—believe me, I knew nothing

00:24:53.760 --> 00:24:56.630
about the Holy Spirit. I knew nothing

00:24:56.640 --> 00:25:00.390
whatsoever

00:25:00.400 --> 00:25:02.549
about the third person of the Trinity.

00:25:02.559 --> 00:25:05.269
Nothing.

00:25:05.279 --> 00:25:07.110
I don't even remember who the preacher

00:25:07.120 --> 00:25:09.190
was; I don't remember one thing that he

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:12.310
said. I've never seen anyone accept

00:25:12.320 --> 00:25:13.830
Christ as their Savior in that Methodist

00:25:13.840 --> 00:25:15.110
church. I'm not sure that anyone was

00:25:15.120 --> 00:25:21.190
converted before or since. I'm not sure.

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:23.269
But suddenly, as they were singing the

00:25:23.279 --> 00:25:26.549
last hymn and I had the Methodist

00:25:26.549 --> 00:25:26.559
hymnal

00:25:26.559 --> 00:25:30.710
in my hand, I began to shake. It was

00:25:30.720 --> 00:25:32.630
years later that I recognized it as the

00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:35.190
power of the Holy Spirit, and I began to

00:25:35.200 --> 00:25:37.909
shake

00:25:37.919 --> 00:25:40.470
so much that I laid the hymnal down and

00:25:40.480 --> 00:25:42.230
then I knew that I had to do something.

00:25:42.240 --> 00:25:45.590
I did the only

00:25:45.600 --> 00:25:49.269
thing that I knew to do:

00:25:49.279 --> 00:25:52.070
I slipped out from that pew and sat down

00:25:52.080 --> 00:25:55.510
on the front row, on the front pew. And

00:25:55.520 --> 00:25:58.950
nobody knew what to do with me.

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:05.029
The preacher didn't know, and I cried.

00:26:05.039 --> 00:26:07.510
What a joy.

00:26:07.520 --> 00:26:08.870
One of the old sisters came to me and

00:26:08.870 --> 00:26:08.880
said,

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:09.990
"Oh, Kathryn, don't

00:26:09.990 --> 00:26:10.000
cry."I

00:26:10.000 --> 00:26:12.663
didn't have a hanky, I remember that,

00:26:12.663 --> 00:26:12.673
and

00:26:12.673 --> 00:26:14.310
my

00:26:14.320 --> 00:26:15.990
tears were running, my nose was running.

00:26:16.000 --> 00:26:18.230
And she gave me a handkerchief and she

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:20.070
said, "Oh, Kathryn, you've been such a

00:26:20.080 --> 00:26:21.909
good girl all your life, don't

00:26:21.909 --> 00:26:21.919
cry."And

00:26:21.919 --> 00:26:27.830
both of us knew she was lying, because

00:26:27.830 --> 00:26:27.840
those

00:26:27.840 --> 00:26:29.909
things didn't happen in Concordia;

00:26:29.919 --> 00:26:36.549
I made them happen.

00:26:36.559 --> 00:26:40.870
That marvelous experience of being born

00:26:40.880 --> 00:26:42.390
again,

00:26:42.400 --> 00:26:48.789
that glorious experience.

00:26:48.799 --> 00:26:52.230
So help me, there's never been a moment

00:26:52.240 --> 00:26:54.950
since that

00:26:54.950 --> 00:26:54.960
experience—that

00:26:54.960 --> 00:26:58.470
Sunday morning in that little

00:26:58.480 --> 00:27:01.750
Methodist church in that front pew when

00:27:01.760 --> 00:27:03.510
I was born again—there's never been a

00:27:03.520 --> 00:27:05.909
split second that I've ever doubted

00:27:05.919 --> 00:27:10.870
my salvation.

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:13.990
And sitting there two weeks ago in that

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:17.110
same pew, I relived many things. I

00:27:17.120 --> 00:27:19.190
remember as a little girl standing there,

00:27:19.200 --> 00:27:20.630
and the only time Papa ever went to

00:27:20.630 --> 00:27:20.640
church—he

00:27:20.640 --> 00:27:24.230
would never go to church; my

00:27:24.240 --> 00:27:29.190
Papa hated preachers.

00:27:29.200 --> 00:27:30.710
If he saw the preacher coming down the

00:27:30.720 --> 00:27:33.269
street, and if he saw the preacher before

00:27:33.279 --> 00:27:35.029
the preacher saw him, the preacher never

00:27:35.039 --> 00:27:41.269
saw him.

00:27:41.279 --> 00:27:47.430
He went to church only

00:27:47.440 --> 00:27:51.430
at Christmas time when his girl

00:27:51.440 --> 00:27:54.470
would give a recitation

00:27:54.470 --> 00:27:54.480
on

00:27:54.480 --> 00:27:59.269
Children's Day when she sang a song.

00:27:59.279 --> 00:28:03.430
They always said that

00:28:03.430 --> 00:28:03.440
Kathryn

00:28:03.440 --> 00:28:09.430
was the apple of her Papa's eye.

00:28:09.440 --> 00:28:12.149
I've heard that ever since I was a

00:28:12.159 --> 00:28:17.830
little girl:

00:28:17.840 --> 00:28:21.590
"You know,

00:28:21.590 --> 00:28:21.600
Kathryn,

00:28:21.600 --> 00:28:23.590
that mean little girl with the freckled

00:28:23.600 --> 00:28:31.190
face and the red hair

00:28:31.200 --> 00:28:35.029
is the apple of her Papa's

00:28:35.039 --> 00:28:38.230
eye."And

00:28:38.240 --> 00:28:41.269
I knew it,

00:28:41.279 --> 00:28:45.430
and it was my security.

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:47.669
I knew it. And every time I got up to

00:28:47.679 --> 00:28:51.029
give that recitation, I saw only one

00:28:51.039 --> 00:28:52.950
person in that little church, and that was

00:28:52.960 --> 00:28:55.269
Papa.

00:28:55.279 --> 00:28:58.870
And I did my best

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:02.549
for Papa;

00:29:02.559 --> 00:29:09.029
I was the apple of his eye.

00:29:13.200 --> 00:29:18.470
And sitting there two weeks ago

00:29:18.470 --> 00:29:18.480
in

00:29:18.480 --> 00:29:21.269
that same pew, three rows from the

00:29:21.279 --> 00:29:22.710
front, where the Holy Spirit first spoke

00:29:22.720 --> 00:29:27.590
to my heart, I sat there in silence

00:29:27.600 --> 00:29:29.510
and it seemed like all the years of my

00:29:29.520 --> 00:29:39.909
life came before me.

00:29:39.909 --> 00:29:39.919
There

00:29:39.919 --> 00:29:43.990
were the turkey houses

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:49.909
where I slept when I first started out.

00:29:49.919 --> 00:29:55.830
I slept in a straw stack once.

00:29:55.840 --> 00:29:59.430
I lived on butter horns for a week—that was

00:29:59.440 --> 00:30:03.909
all I could afford. There

00:30:03.909 --> 00:30:03.919
have

00:30:03.919 --> 00:30:08.870
been deep waters,

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:11.510
very deep waters.

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:18.470
The sun hasn't always

00:30:18.470 --> 00:30:18.480
shone.

00:30:18.480 --> 00:30:21.830
And I sat there and I thought,

00:30:21.840 --> 00:30:24.389
"What through all of these years really

00:30:24.399 --> 00:30:27.430
has been the motivating force in this

00:30:27.440 --> 00:30:34.389
life of

00:30:34.389 --> 00:30:34.399
mine?"I

00:30:34.399 --> 00:30:37.750
wasn't made to do what I've done all

00:30:37.760 --> 00:30:40.870
my life.

00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:42.710
There wasn't enough money in the whole

00:30:42.720 --> 00:30:47.669
world to pay me for the long hours and

00:30:47.679 --> 00:30:51.590
the sleepless nights. Believe me, I tell

00:30:51.600 --> 00:30:56.870
you the truth,

00:30:56.880 --> 00:30:59.909
there's not enough money in the world to

00:30:59.919 --> 00:31:04.310
pay me

00:31:04.320 --> 00:31:09.750
for the way I've worked in my lifetime.

00:31:09.760 --> 00:31:16.470
Nobody forced me to do it.

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:19.029
It wasn't because of doctrine; it wasn't

00:31:19.039 --> 00:31:23.350
because I was afraid of God.

00:31:23.360 --> 00:31:28.870
I didn't do it because I feared

00:31:28.870 --> 00:31:28.880
God—I'm

00:31:28.880 --> 00:31:32.710
not that kind of a person.

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:38.070
I'm just not that kind of a person.

00:31:38.080 --> 00:31:41.669
I didn't do it because somebody told me

00:31:41.679 --> 00:31:51.029
to do it.

00:31:51.039 --> 00:31:53.990
I've had one

00:31:54.000 --> 00:31:57.830
verse of scripture

00:31:57.840 --> 00:32:01.110
that I've wept over;

00:32:01.120 --> 00:32:05.350
I've held it closely to me,

00:32:05.360 --> 00:32:11.029
and it's been the motivating force

00:32:11.039 --> 00:32:15.750
of my life.

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:20.470
I read it to you:

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:24.230
"Keep me

00:32:24.240 --> 00:32:33.350
as the apple of the eye;

00:32:33.360 --> 00:32:37.430
hide me

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:45.029
under thy

00:32:45.029 --> 00:32:45.039
wings."A

00:32:45.039 --> 00:32:50.149
million times I've held this precious

00:32:50.159 --> 00:32:57.590
word to my heart.

00:32:57.600 --> 00:33:01.590
I knew the security that there was

00:33:01.600 --> 00:33:07.430
in being the apple of Papa's eye.

00:33:07.440 --> 00:33:10.070
I never feared his wrath.

00:33:10.080 --> 00:33:13.430
Papa never laid a hand on me. Never.

00:33:13.440 --> 00:33:15.269
Not that I didn't need it, but he didn't

00:33:15.279 --> 00:33:18.149
do it.

00:33:18.159 --> 00:33:22.789
My Papa never laid a hand on me.

00:33:22.799 --> 00:33:25.590
All Papa had to do was just look at me a

00:33:25.600 --> 00:33:28.310
certain way—that's all. He would get

00:33:28.320 --> 00:33:32.950
just a certain look on his face,

00:33:32.960 --> 00:33:39.509
and I knew it was a look of disapproval.

00:33:39.519 --> 00:33:46.870
And I loved him so much.

00:33:46.880 --> 00:33:52.149
I was the apple of his eye,

00:33:52.159 --> 00:33:57.830
and I wasn't going to let him down.

00:34:05.519 --> 00:34:08.149
A million times,

00:34:08.149 --> 00:34:08.159
methinks,

00:34:08.159 --> 00:34:10.790
I've held this close to my

00:34:10.800 --> 00:34:14.069
heart

00:34:14.079 --> 00:34:15.829
and I said, "Wonderful Jesus, more than

00:34:15.839 --> 00:34:18.550
anything else in the whole world,

00:34:18.560 --> 00:34:24.550
I want to be the apple of your

00:34:24.550 --> 00:34:24.560
eye."I

00:34:24.560 --> 00:34:27.190
have but one ambition in

00:34:27.190 --> 00:34:27.200
life—just

00:34:27.200 --> 00:34:29.270
one,

00:34:29.280 --> 00:34:33.349
only one. I live for one thing and one

00:34:33.359 --> 00:34:35.909
thing

00:34:35.909 --> 00:34:35.919
only—just

00:34:35.919 --> 00:34:39.909
one thing.

00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:48.550
Just one thing

00:34:48.560 --> 00:34:51.430
I desire, but one thing above everything

00:34:51.440 --> 00:35:01.990
else in the world:

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:05.670
to be the apple

00:35:05.680 --> 00:35:17.430
of your eye.

00:35:17.440 --> 00:35:21.750
I want your smile.

00:35:21.760 --> 00:35:23.990
It's beautiful.

00:35:24.000 --> 00:35:26.470
It blesses me so. I think I've listened

00:35:26.480 --> 00:35:29.589
to that, I can't tell you how many times,

00:35:29.599 --> 00:35:31.190
going over and over and just

00:35:31.200 --> 00:35:35.510
thinking about what she's saying.

00:35:35.520 --> 00:35:37.990
And you look at

00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:40.150
somebody who walked with Him the way she

00:35:40.160 --> 00:35:43.750
did in a modern age, you know, and

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:45.510
that's why my friend Billy Burke was

00:35:45.520 --> 00:35:48.630
mentored by her, and thank God he's been

00:35:48.640 --> 00:35:50.710
a friend to me,

00:35:50.720 --> 00:35:56.870
because

00:35:56.870 --> 00:35:56.880
it's

00:35:56.880 --> 00:35:59.750
cross-pollination.

00:35:59.760 --> 00:36:03.910
There's so much about

00:36:03.910 --> 00:36:03.920
cross-pollination.

00:36:03.920 --> 00:36:07.829
You can feel it; it changes you.

00:36:07.839 --> 00:36:09.589
And I know it's all the Holy Spirit, and

00:36:09.599 --> 00:36:11.430
He changes you from the

00:36:11.440 --> 00:36:13.990
inside out by the Word of God. But there

00:36:14.000 --> 00:36:15.670
is a lot about

00:36:15.670 --> 00:36:15.680
cross-pollination

00:36:15.680 --> 00:36:17.990
when you get around

00:36:18.000 --> 00:36:21.030
people that have been around it,

00:36:23.599 --> 00:36:27.349
the presence changes you. You

00:36:27.359 --> 00:36:28.950
get around people. It's like, who are

00:36:28.960 --> 00:36:31.270
you hanging around? I used to see all

00:36:31.280 --> 00:36:33.670
the time, "Who are you hanging

00:36:33.670 --> 00:36:33.680
around?"I'll

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:35.829
tell you where you'll

00:36:35.839 --> 00:36:37.510
be in the next couple of years by who

00:36:37.520 --> 00:36:38.710
you're hanging around, what books

00:36:38.720 --> 00:36:39.910
you're reading, what you're watching

00:36:39.920 --> 00:36:46.310
on TV, and what you're meditating on.

00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:49.270
You must come up higher

00:36:49.280 --> 00:36:54.470
in your walk with the Father in 2026.

00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:56.870
But I bring all this to you because

00:36:56.880 --> 00:37:00.230
it's what has helped me,

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:03.670
and so people are always asking. So, I

00:37:03.680 --> 00:37:05.750
just try to put you in the direction of...

00:37:05.760 --> 00:37:09.030
and I had

00:37:09.040 --> 00:37:10.630
somebody email me and said, "Brandon,

00:37:10.640 --> 00:37:12.230
you can't talk about finances. You

00:37:12.240 --> 00:37:13.430
shouldn't do

00:37:13.430 --> 00:37:13.440
that."Listen,

00:37:13.440 --> 00:37:17.349
I tell you what I hear.

00:37:17.359 --> 00:37:19.349
I'm not a financial adviser. I'm not

00:37:19.359 --> 00:37:22.230
trying to manipulate markets.

00:37:22.240 --> 00:37:24.550
Whatever you think you are saying to me,

00:37:24.560 --> 00:37:28.150
I see these things. And I tell

00:37:28.160 --> 00:37:29.990
you, you take it to God in prayer. If

00:37:30.000 --> 00:37:32.069
you don't feel like it's the Lord, then

00:37:32.079 --> 00:37:33.430
you say, "Brandon, I feel like you're

00:37:33.430 --> 00:37:33.440
off."And

00:37:33.440 --> 00:37:35.910
you know what? Guess what?

00:37:38.079 --> 00:37:40.630
I could be. I'm just as human as every

00:37:40.640 --> 00:37:42.790
single one of you.

00:37:42.800 --> 00:37:46.710
Can I miss it? Yes. Am I perfect? No,

00:37:46.720 --> 00:37:50.310
not by a long shot. But whenever I

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:52.150
bring it to you, it's just

00:37:52.160 --> 00:37:53.829
something that was dear to my heart that

00:37:53.839 --> 00:37:55.829
I've been praying over about Don Jr.

00:37:55.839 --> 00:37:58.710
here and Eric Trump and all the

00:37:58.720 --> 00:38:00.150
Trump family, and the Lord said, "I'm

00:38:00.160 --> 00:38:01.829
going to multiply their wealth times

00:38:01.829 --> 00:38:01.839
three."So,

00:38:01.839 --> 00:38:04.550
you can do with what you

00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:06.470
want, but it's not for you to take

00:38:06.480 --> 00:38:08.390
and invest your hard-earned money into

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:10.230
something whenever you haven't prayed

00:38:10.240 --> 00:38:12.230
about it yourself. How foolish are you

00:38:12.240 --> 00:38:14.230
to do that?

00:38:14.240 --> 00:38:16.470
I'm not trying to tell you to do that; I

00:38:16.480 --> 00:38:19.510
ask you to pray with it. Help me.

00:38:19.520 --> 00:38:21.990
But it's all in my opinion and it's

00:38:22.000 --> 00:38:24.390
never financial advice.

00:38:24.400 --> 00:38:25.990
But there are so many people asking about

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:27.750
what you said about the Prince of

00:38:27.760 --> 00:38:30.310
Persia and about Babylon and the dinar

00:38:30.320 --> 00:38:32.069
rising and all the things. It's

00:38:32.079 --> 00:38:35.910
biblical. It's in the word.

00:38:35.920 --> 00:38:37.750
I'm not trying to tell you what to do

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:39.990
with your finances. That would be the

00:38:40.000 --> 00:38:41.990
last person to listen to about that. I

00:38:42.000 --> 00:38:44.950
don't have a degree in that.

00:38:44.960 --> 00:38:47.030
I just follow the voice of the Lord as

00:38:47.040 --> 00:38:49.910
closely as I know how.

00:38:49.920 --> 00:38:51.829
And I'm just as human as anybody

00:38:51.839 --> 00:38:53.990
else.

00:38:54.000 --> 00:38:57.510
So, take it for what you

00:38:57.520 --> 00:38:59.589
want, pray about it. Let's pray

00:38:59.599 --> 00:39:01.750
together and see

00:39:01.760 --> 00:39:04.550
what the Lord wants us to do here. When I was with you

00:39:04.550 --> 00:39:04.560
all this morning, I saw to

00:39:04.560 --> 00:39:07.270
pray over

00:39:10.480 --> 00:39:13.030
the churches,

00:39:13.040 --> 00:39:14.790
mega-churches,

00:39:14.800 --> 00:39:16.710
movie

00:39:16.720 --> 00:39:19.430
theaters,

00:39:19.440 --> 00:39:23.510
major gatherings of

00:39:23.520 --> 00:39:26.710
all kinds, praying over this Red Dawn

00:39:26.720 --> 00:39:28.390
experience that the Lord keeps talking

00:39:28.400 --> 00:39:32.390
to us about, praying over

00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:35.190
D-Day

00:39:35.200 --> 00:39:39.030
as we have attacked Venezuela today

00:39:39.040 --> 00:39:41.750
and all the things the Lord showed us. I

00:39:41.760 --> 00:39:42.950
thought it was interesting because

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:45.109
President Trump said that he

00:39:45.119 --> 00:39:49.589
put so many troops on the ground.

00:39:49.599 --> 00:39:54.630
Was that to secure the oil wells?

00:39:54.640 --> 00:39:56.550
There's a lot more to this that the Lord

00:39:56.560 --> 00:40:00.470
shows me, but I told you I saw all

00:40:00.480 --> 00:40:03.750
the oil wells catching fire

00:40:03.760 --> 00:40:08.630
and there was a retaliation against

00:40:08.640 --> 00:40:11.670
the United States of America in the

00:40:11.680 --> 00:40:14.069
days ahead because of

00:40:14.079 --> 00:40:16.230
the oil. Now, I want to play this little

00:40:16.240 --> 00:40:17.910
clip for you—just this one little clip

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:19.829
of what President Trump said out of his

00:40:19.839 --> 00:40:22.390
mouth to confirm what the Holy Spirit

00:40:22.400 --> 00:40:26.390
told us about why they went in

00:40:26.400 --> 00:40:28.310
and attacked Venezuela in the

00:40:28.320 --> 00:40:29.670
first place. I said, "You think it's

00:40:29.680 --> 00:40:32.390
about just drugs? 10% is about

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:39.190
cocaine. This other is about

00:40:39.200 --> 00:40:40.950
right here."I want you to see this. This

00:40:40.960 --> 00:40:42.630
was said today:

00:40:42.640 --> 00:40:45.510
"You know, they stole our oil. We

00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:46.950
built that whole

00:40:46.960 --> 00:40:49.430
industry there and they just took it

00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:51.030
over like we were nothing. And we had a

00:40:51.040 --> 00:40:52.630
president that decided not to do

00:40:52.640 --> 00:40:54.310
anything about it. They were pumping

00:40:54.320 --> 00:40:56.470
almost nothing by comparison to what

00:40:56.480 --> 00:40:59.430
they could have been pumping and what

00:40:59.440 --> 00:41:01.670
could have taken place. We're going to

00:41:01.680 --> 00:41:05.589
have our very large United States oil

00:41:05.599 --> 00:41:07.510
companies, the biggest anywhere in the

00:41:07.520 --> 00:41:10.870
world, go in, spend billions of dollars,

00:41:10.880 --> 00:41:13.829
fix the badly broken infrastructure, the

00:41:13.839 --> 00:41:15.990
oil infrastructure, and start making

00:41:16.000 --> 00:41:17.510
money for the country.

00:41:17.520 --> 00:41:23.109
We must put a kink in the

00:41:23.109 --> 00:41:23.119
hose."So,

00:41:23.119 --> 00:41:25.190
he already said what the Holy Spirit

00:41:25.200 --> 00:41:26.630
told us was going to happen to us about

00:41:26.640 --> 00:41:29.430
the war. And I saw the United

00:41:29.440 --> 00:41:32.870
States of America building

00:41:32.880 --> 00:41:36.390
a major military

00:41:36.400 --> 00:41:39.270
base in Venezuela, and they would occupy

00:41:39.280 --> 00:41:41.910
Venezuela in the days ahead. And I

00:41:41.920 --> 00:41:45.270
saw us

00:41:45.270 --> 00:41:45.280
setting

00:41:45.280 --> 00:41:48.630
up a proxy

00:41:48.640 --> 00:41:51.270
government. The United States

00:41:51.280 --> 00:41:53.750
would govern over this.

00:41:53.760 --> 00:41:57.829
And I saw it turning red, which I

00:41:57.839 --> 00:42:00.630
thought was interesting.

00:42:00.640 --> 00:42:03.109
And then the Lord showed me that

00:42:03.119 --> 00:42:05.270
great revival would break forth in

00:42:05.280 --> 00:42:07.190
Venezuela and that they would bring

00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:09.190
forth economy and stability and things

00:42:09.200 --> 00:42:13.190
like that. Well, this is exactly what we

00:42:13.200 --> 00:42:15.109
tried to do to Iraq, but that failed

00:42:15.119 --> 00:42:18.710
miserably, didn't it?

00:42:18.720 --> 00:42:21.829
Let's see how this goes. I think

00:42:21.839 --> 00:42:23.510
it's interesting because the Lord said

00:42:23.520 --> 00:42:25.750
he would be like a Gaddafi, like a

00:42:25.760 --> 00:42:29.270
Saddam Hussein, and he would be removed.

00:42:29.280 --> 00:42:31.589
Now, I know each one of those men came

00:42:31.599 --> 00:42:34.870
to their death. Will this man? I

00:42:34.880 --> 00:42:37.109
don't know. I think it could be

00:42:37.119 --> 00:42:39.109
a type and shadow, a metaphor of

00:42:39.119 --> 00:42:41.109
what the Lord was showing me—that these

00:42:41.119 --> 00:42:43.109
people were moved out of being

00:42:43.119 --> 00:42:45.670
head over their nations and then all of

